otlp.description:
OTLP exporters for usage data. Sends usage records as OTLP log records to one or more OpenTelemetry-compatible backends. Each entry creates an independent exporter, allowing fan-out to multiple destinations.

```toml [[observability.usage.otlp]] name = "grafana" endpoint = "https://otlp-gateway.grafana.net/otlp" headers = { Authorization = "Basic xxx" }

[[observability.usage.otlp]] name = "datadog" endpoint = "https://otel.datadoghq.com" headers = { "DD-API-KEY" = "xxx" } ```
